Job Description
Working closely with a leading provider of Marine Propulsion Systems, our client is expanding its commercial team with the hiring of a Regional Sales Manager. This is a new position based in Singapore and the opportunity has arisen as a result of the client expanding their distribution capabilities in the Asia region. We are looking for an ambitious individual with strong Maritime background within a sales capacity.As the Regional Sales Manager, you report to the Global Manager and actively drive revenue through direct sales and channel management. You will draw on extensive business development experience, especially in Asia Maritime markets and identify tender opportunities, pre-qualify requirements and work in-hand with engineering and execution teams to win new projects.You should have at least 4 years’ experience in a similar capacity and excellent knowledge of the Marine industry. Technical experience is an added advantage. This position offers a competitive salary and an expansive platform to take charge of your own performance and development.If this sounds like a opportunity you are interested in, please contact Ambrose Chan at
